## 5. Vulnerability Management Plan

Per FDA 2023 Premarket Cybersecurity Guidance:

- [ ] All identified vulnerabilities have been assessed for patient safety impact
- [ ] Unpatched critical/high vulnerabilities have documented risk acceptances with clinical justification
- [ ] A postmarket vulnerability monitoring plan is in place (MedSBOM `watch` command recommended)
- [ ] Software update/patch deployment procedures are documented
- [ ] Coordinated vulnerability disclosure process is established

